=============
gg_tom_warehouse
=============
A cold themed warehouse, focused around several stacks of secured crates. Vents pour freezing air into the warehouse, keeping whatever secrets frozen. Homemade ladders traverse some of the stacks, while weak beams can help get to the remaining stacks. A nice sized map for any amount of players.
=============
Other: 32 Slot, soundscape & no full bright.

Please do not edit and/or include in any packs. w/o permission.
=============
